name: Tree of Life Necklace
description:
Belle Histoire = Beautiful Story

In truth, Belle Histoire is simply, Beautiful Music...please visit their Facebook Page here: 
http://www.facebook.com/home.php#!/bellehistoiremusic

And listen to their EP, Spirits...it's amazing...and that's why I choose to support this new musical endeavor.

The "Branch Out' necklace is designed with a dainty tree pendant in either antique bronze, accented with a golden agate bead; or silver, accented with a freshwater pearl.

Both necklaces hang from matching metal 1.5mm ball chains and arrive in an organza bag.

name: Ollivander's Express
description:
Consider this your express stop to finding the perfect wand...in minature scale and jewelry form.

This tibetan silver wand is accented with dark beads and hangs from a silver plated chain.

Enjoy!

name: SK8RBOI Earrings & Necklace
description:
Yup, I did, I went there...and you can too with these adorable earrings and necklace.

Tiny Tibetan silver skateboards daintily from stainless steel earwires... ready for summer fun!

The necklace is matching skateboard accented with tiny "Tech Deck" wheels and hematite beads.

Enjoy!

name: Antique Fan Necklace
description:
Love the name??

It's quite romantic, isn't it? It means Beautiful Story...

The music of Belle Histoire is here can be found here... 
http://www.facebook.com/home.php#!/bellehistoiremusic

And you should buy their EP Spirits...

You can also support them, by purchasing one (or more!) of these necklaces...

A petite antique electric fan is available in either silver or antique bronze. The silver fan is adorned with a tiny hematite bead and seed pearl bead. The bronze fan is accented with a tiny brown glass bead and a seed pearl bead.

The pendants hang from a 1.5mm ball link chain in a matching metal.

When purchasing, please note BRONZE or SILVER!

name: 3D Bee
description:
A silver bee sits atop a unique antiqued brass design in this great summer necklace!

Bee pendant is approximately 1.25 inches E/W by 1 inch N/S and is raised approximately 1/4 inch.

Mr. Bee hangs from a silvertone curb link chain, length is your choice when you purchase.
